Package: echosmart-gateway
Version: 1.0.0
Architecture: arm64
Maintainer: EchoSmart <support@echosmart.io>
Description: EchoSmart Gateway for Raspberry Pi
 IoT gateway for precision agriculture sensor monitoring.
 Includes Python gateway service and optimized C++ sensor binaries.
 .
 Supported sensors:
  - DS18B20 (1-Wire temperature)
  - DHT22 (GPIO temperature + humidity)
  - BH1750 (I2C ambient light)
  - Capacitive soil moisture via ADS1115 (I2C ADC)
  - MH-Z19C (UART CO2)
 .
 Communicates with EchoSmart Cloud via MQTT and REST API.
 Stores data locally in SQLite for offline operation.
Depends: python3 (>= 3.9),
         python3-pip,
         python3-venv,
         libgpiod2,
         python3-libgpiod,
         i2c-tools,
         mosquitto,
         mosquitto-clients,
         sqlite3,
         curl,
         adduser
Recommends: pigpio,
            python3-pigpio
Suggests: avahi-daemon
